content: I'm looking for a reviewer for https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/85706/files? Can anyone help with that or suggest a good person?
@nagisa I'm a bit confused about what you want though. Do you want eliminate_frame_pointer = false moved into apple_base.rs and removed from all of the places that use apple_base?
Ah, I missed this is using a generic apple_base and not aarch64 specific apple_base. Fine to leave the code as is, then.
Though it would still be good to find _some_ way to make sure this is shared between aarch64 apples somehow.
Doesn't need to happen in this PR though.
So if you'll just update the PR description its good to go.
@nagisa I ended up making the change to just set it to false in apple_base and removing it from all the other places
I'm pretty sure aarch64 darwin was the only place enabling it
